'''''Star Wars Insider'' 82''' was the 82nd issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'', released in [[May]] [[2005]].

It started shipping to subscribers on [[May 17]], and began shipping to newsstands on [[May 30]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]"
*"[[Skywalking]]: News from Around the Galaxy" {{C|by [[Mary Franklin]] and Brett Rector}}
*"[[Jedi Library (department)|Jedi Library]]" &mdash; Apprentice To The ''Sith'' Wizards {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
*"[[Drawn by the Force]]" &mdash; [[Star Wars: Visionaries|Artistic Splinter Cells]] {{C|by Daniel Wallace}}
*"[[Set Piece|Technical Readout]]" &mdash; Rebel Blockade Runner: ''Tantive IV'' {{C|by [[Chris Trevas]]}}
*"[[Star Wars Q&A|Ask the Master]]"&mdash; A Grab Bag of Lightsabers {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]}}
*"[[Anchorhead Arcade]]" &mdash; It's All the Rage! {{C|by [[Sid Shuman]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" &mdash; Midnight Madness Plus "48 Hours" Equals No Sleep {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet|Steve Sansweet]]}}
*"[[Jabba's Collection]]" &mdash; Experience The [[Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith (toy line)|''Star Wars'' Evolution]] {{C|by Brett Rector}}
*"[[Best of Hyperspace]]" {{C|by Pablo Hidalgo and [[Bonnie Burton]]}}
*[[Bantha Tracks (department)|''Bantha Tracks'']] Vol. 13 {{C|by Mary Franklin}}
*"[[Laugh It Up, Fuzzball]]" {{C|by [[Randy Martinez]]}}

===Features===
*"[[The Starships of Episode III]]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*:<small>'''Insider''' takes a closer look at some of the [[Starship/Legends|ships]] featured in [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|Episode III]].</small>
*"[[The Dark Lord Cometh]]" {{C|by [[Brett Rector]]}}
*:<small>[[Hayden Christensen]] is interviewed about playing the central character of the entire '''Star Wars''' saga.</small>
*"[[The Evil Within]]" {{C|by Brett Rector}}
*:<small>In an exclusive '''Insider''' interview, [[Ian McDiarmid]] reveals some interesting details about [[Palpatine/Legends|Darth Sidious]] and his relationship with [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]].</small>
*"[[Queen Mother of the Galaxy]]" {{C|by Brett Rector}}
*:<small>[[Natalie Portman]] is interviewed about her role in Revenge of the Sith.</small>

